thread.title: RONALD

author: RONALD
title: RONALD
text: Upon receiving the package of Ink Cartridges, I put in the Black ink, because that's what goes first, and within 2 days, I noticed the printing was coming up lighter and lighter. Upon Rechecking the Cartridge, I noticed that the Black ink was leaking. I took it out, and put back a Brothers Cartridge. Printer just got worst. I noticed that their was ink all over the place, so I put it on Manuel Cleaning, and then put in a NEW Bk Cartridge that was sent to me as a replacement, and EVERYTHING NOW seems to be working just fine. What started out bad, ENDED UP WELL! I will continue to use the Inkfarm products going forward.
